StringLiteralExpr.value: The following fields are required, unless they are grayed out (Selecting ''user-defined'' choice is not recommended):

If obtained ''info'' from MATLAB Mapping Toolbox''s geotiffinfo.m, you can set the fields above like this: PixelScale.X=info.PixelScale(1); PixelScale.Y=info.PixelScale(2); PixelScale.Z=info.PixelScale(3);
Tiepoint.X=info.TiePoints.WorldPoints.X; (info.TiePoints.WorldPoints(1) in old MATLAB); Tiepoint.Y=info.TiePoints.WorldPoints.Y; (info.TiePoints.WorldPoints(2) in old MATLAB); Tiepoint.Z=0;
ModelType=info.ModelType; but please keep: Tiepoint.I=0; Tiepoint.J=0; Tiepoint.K=0; instead of info.TiePoints.ImagePoints.
The following fields are optional, please select or fill whatever you know (Avoid using ''user-defined'', if possible):
The following fields are optional and for user-defined only, please DO NOT fill those that you are not sure:
Make sure that the required fields are selected or filled, unless they are grayed out.
